  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/a98cc5090dc2223610026feed545a3af.poster.avif?t=1766435803\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/a98cc5090dc2223610026feed545a3af.webm?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/3530c7f540c5c17245d56039e1676d53.poster.avif?t=1766435803\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/3530c7f540c5c17245d56039e1676d53.webm?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something strange is afoot in the small rustic Norwegian town of Skogdal... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/bf1ea6e0d5d1604913702ffeff201937.poster.avif?t=1766435803\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/bf1ea6e0d5d1604913702ffeff201937.webm?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/bf1ea6e0d5d1604913702ffeff201937.mp4?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a deckbuilding card game where you have to explore a large hand-crafted world across multiple runs. Immerse yourself in this weird but familiar adventure, and uncover an unsettling Carpenter-esque mystery…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/15b3339ab3af7390096b99c78264674b.poster.avif?t=1766435803\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/15b3339ab3af7390096b99c78264674b.webm?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/15b3339ab3af7390096b99c78264674b.mp4?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skogdal offers more than 300 different cards for you to discover and draft. Fuse cards, build powerful combos and recruit followers to aid you in your journey: politicians, bodybuilders, wrestlers, pyromaniacs, skaters, punks, priests, pets and pests…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/9cba8a61259ba742b6b6ed655752a7e7.poster.avif?t=1766435803\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/9cba8a61259ba742b6b6ed655752a7e7.webm?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/9cba8a61259ba742b6b6ed655752a7e7.mp4?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...good luck, the truth is out there!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/34c412e4f3093cac9a9d147870a18947.poster.avif?t=1766435803\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/34c412e4f3093cac9a9d147870a18947.webm?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2452820/extras/34c412e4f3093cac9a9d147870a18947.mp4?t=1766435803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
